name: LongActingMuscarinicAntagonistsLAMAAllergyIntolerance
title: Long Acting Muscarinic Antagonists (LAMA) Allergy Intolerance
purpose: (Clinical Focus: SNOMED CT codes and RxNORM codes that could be returned by the FHIR Allergy Intolerance resource, and would indicate allergy or intolerance to LAMA medications),(Data Element Scope: ALLERGY_INTOLERANCE:LAMA),(Inclusion Criteria: RxNORM codes for individual medications that are LAMA medications, and various SNOMED CT codes that would indicate allergy or intolerance to LAMA medications as a class, or individual LAMA medications),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
